{
  "description": "3D arcade-hall FRAME: composes hero-nav (free roam) + arcade-play (token/ticket economy) + fx-particles + arcade-flow (win/lose) onto one shared GameState with a single render authority. Games consume this molecule and supply only theme/assets/units/tiles/machines via config.",
